{"tid":922083,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人認為應該移除留言正負皮","createTime":"2018-11-30T05:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T05:40:30.000Z","uid":199048,"like":8,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2d17a33277d92805faa143f43f61d0d9fab03573","tid":922083,"uid":199048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T05:30:51.000Z","msg":"成個post既正負皮還好<br />\n起碼唔會一面倒得咁厲害<br />\n起碼啲人都識留言評論下<br />\n<br />\n但留言正負皮真係好過份<br />\n99%都清一色正/負皮<br />\n剩低果個禁錯制<br />\n然後啲人入黎一望  咁多正/負皮<br />\n就先入為主覺得岩/錯<br />\n尤其呢到啲人一啲獨立思考都冇<br />\n主流覺得乜佢就覺得乜<br />\n<br />\n成個post頓時變得毫冇討論價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好鬼低汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1793cd4000b86aabe438fdc719ab8f4346c44b3","tid":922083,"uid":21423,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T05:31:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4fe88ce6b371dd36cae2fabe664857c4d99778a","tid":922083,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T05:32:57.000Z","msg":"有無諗過本身個POST就無討論價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392d4f7902f1f149dd82043fe82de96c0907248c","tid":922083,"uid":199048,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T05:35:07.000Z","msg":"點解直接冇左#2個留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7970aa31aa2dcf809675875f7fb8635031daa7a1","tid":922083,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T05:36:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"307a956bc6537f3fbcd2b997afef9f5b85966b95","tid":922083,"uid":153136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T05:37:58.000Z","msg":"直接評完先可以睇結果咪得囉"},{"pid":"d0ded68f8e47920051abdb969d4e1c6425e57b85","tid":922083,"uid":175732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote"